Package: pathToHere
Title: Convert File Path to here::here()
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Will", "Drysdale", , "will.drysdale@york.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Its hard to use RStudios file path autocomplete with the here package.
             This package provides an addin that takes a file path string and 
             replaces it with a call to here(). 
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    rstudioapi,
    stringr
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
